'''Okanagan Dirt Riders''' ('''ODR Racing''') is a [[Canada|Canadian]] [[off-road racing]] series started by George Madarasz in 2002.  The [[Canadian Motorcycle Association]] (CMA) sanctioned series became the benchmark in the Canadian racing scene and established new talent and possibilities for the sport to grow.

