{{Infobox Magazine | title = Стършел | publisher =Стършел ООД | category = [[Satire]] and [[humor]] | total_circulation = | frequency = Weekly | language = [[Bulgarian language|Bulgarian]] | editor = Mikhail Veshim | editor_title =Editor in chief | founded = 1886 | firstdate = | country = [[Bulgaria]] | based = [[Sofia]] | website = http://www.starshel.bg/ | issn =0205-1273 }} '''''Strashel''''' ({{lang-bg|"Стършел"}}, "[[hornet]]") is a [[Humor magazine|satirical magazine]] published in the [[Bulgaria]]. Founded in 1886 and published without interruption since 1946, it is the oldest Bulgarian periodical in continuous circulation.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://e-vestnik.bg/7209|title=Що е „Стършел” свършил за 63 години|date=25 September 2009|accessdate=2 February 2015|work=E-Vestnik}}</ref> The magazines is based in [[Sofia]] and is published on a weekly basis.<ref>{{cite book|title=The Europa World Year Book 2003|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XLvU9lroRuUC&pg=PA897|accessdate=26 July 2015|date=10 July 2003|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-85743-227-5|page=897}}</ref>
